data.description: Beautiful Townhomes Brand New. Many Parks in the Community.   1 Car garage + 2 car driveway, fitting 3 cars at all times.  This beautiful unit is located in the quaint and well-kept Regal Palm Square, an open homeowner association community close  to all major highways  great restaurants and retail stores nearby, This area is gateway point between Miami FL  and the Florida Keys. *Pictures, photographs, features, colors and sizes are approximate for illustration purposes only and will vary from the homes as built.  These photos are not of the actual home but are similar to the home being built.
